1. *Bas* se njih dvoje sreli u parku. (They two met in the park.)
2. *Bas* tada je shvatio da je zaista zaljubljen. (It was then he realized he was really in love.)
3. *Basa* mi je pretežak za preneti. (The basket is too heavy for me to carry.)
4. *Bazu* je izgradio u dvorištu. (He built a base in the yard.)
5. *Basa* je izgubio ključeve. (He lost the keys.)